<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_LIGHTSPEARSMAN">
			<Text>Light Spearman</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_HELP_LIGHTSPEARSMAN">
			<Text>Ancient Era melee unit specializing in quick raids on enemy territory. They are able skirmishers.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LIGHTSPEARSMAN_TEXT">
			<Text>Wearing no armor at all the the Light Spearman is unburdened to sprint through the wilderness.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV5_LIGHTSPEARSMAN_TEXT">
			<Text>Armed with little more than a pointy stick and brute force, The Light Spearman rely on speed and surprise to overtake their foes.</Text>
		</Row>
	<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_BRONZESWORDSMAN">
		<Text>Bronze Swordsman</Text>
	</Row>
	<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_BRONZESWORDSMAN_STRATEGY">
		<Text>The Bronze Swordsman is a strong Ancient era melee unit that doesn't require iron. It upgrades to Longswordsman.</Text>
	</Row>
	<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_HELP_BRONZESWORDSMAN">
		<Text>These Ancient warriors fight hard when iron resources are scarce. They may be weaker than the classical age swordsman but doesn't require iron.</Text>
	</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_LIGHTPIKEMAN">
			<Text>Light Pikeman</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_HELP_LIGHTPIKEMAN">
			<Text>Medieval Era melee unit specializing in quick raids on enemy territory. They are able skirmishers.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LIGHTPIKEMAN_TEXT">
			<Text>Wearing no armor at all the the Light Pikeman is unburdened to outflank their opponents.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV5_LIGHTPIKEMAN_TEXT">
			<Text>Armed with little more than a pointy stick and brute force, The Light Pikeman rely on speed to overtake their foes.</Text>
	</Row>
</Language_en_US>

